# AegisAI — REST smoke examples (VS Code REST Client, IntelliJ HTTP Client, Bruno).
# @base = root URL; set @apiKey when AEGISAI_API_KEY is set.

@base = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@apiKey =
# @apiKey = your-secret

### Health & probes
GET {{base}}/health
GET {{base}}/live
GET {{base}}/ready

### Version
GET {{base}}/version

### Policy (optional auth)
GET {{base}}/v1/policy
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Sync chat
POST {{base}}/v1/query
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "model": "llama3.2",
  "messages": [{ "role": "user", "content": "Ping — reply with OK." }]
}

### Create job (replace file URI with a real path on the API host)
POST {{base}}/v1/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Idempotency-Key: smoke-demo-1

{
  "inputs": [
    { "type": "image_ref", "uri": "file:///absolute/path/to/image.png" },
    { "type": "text", "text": "Describe the image in one sentence." }
  ],
  "sensitivity_label": "internal",
  "mode": "local_only"
}

### Metrics
GET {{base}}/metrics
GET {{base}}/v1/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
